# Real frontend bundle is produced by `make web-ui-embed` (rsync from
# desktop/frontend/dist-web/). dist/ is fully a build product — only
# the .gitkeep marker is tracked so //go:embed all:dist still finds the
# directory in a fresh checkout. The fallback served when dist/ is
# empty lives in ../stub.html (committed, embedded separately).
dist/*
!dist/.gitkeep
